# ğŸ”‘ UNIVERSAL NAMING CONVENTIONS

| Column     | Rule              |
| ---------- | ----------------- |
| timestamps | `_ts` suffix      |
| booleans   | `is_` prefix      |
| keys       | `_id` suffix      |
| dates      | `DATE` not string |
| hashes     | `record_hash`     |

